RESPONSIVENSS
		1. the responsiveness is a concept of displaying any website styles perfectly 
		
		fit for all the devices like mobile, tablet, laptop and extra large screen.
			
			we can achieve responsivenss with meedia queries
			
			1.in the media queries we will define the styles based on the screeen sizes for every devices
				ex : mobile devices
					@media(max-width : 500px){
					body{
					background color: voilet
					}
					}
					
					tablet
					@media(min-width : 501px) and(max-width : 800px){
					body{
					background color: voilet
					}
					}
					
					laptop
					
					@media(min-width : 801px) and(max-width : 1200px){
					body{
					background color: greeen;
					}
					}
					
					extra large
					@media(min-width : 1201px) {
					body{
					background color: blue;
					}
					}
					
					
NOTE : TO ACHIEEVE THE BEST RESPONSIVENSS WE HAVE TO GIVE THE DYNAMIC VALUES LIKE % , rem etc.;
		INSTEAD OF STATIC VALUES  'px' 







